        <mj-text padding="10px 2px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;    
              line-height: 1.5; 
              margin-top:2px;
            ">Did you know the President of the United States receives a top-secret briefing on national security every morning?</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;  
              line-height: 1.5;
            "><strong>In this edition:</strong></p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              padding-left: 10px; 
            ">→ Obesity rising worldwide</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ Opposition smoke bombs parliament</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.5;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ Serena Williams buys Toronto Tempo</p>
        </mj-text> 
