    <!-- Spotlight -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_fsection" background-color="#ffffff" css-class="mj_fsection">
      <mj-column background-color="#ffffff" width="100%">
        <mj-text padding="2px 12px 0px 12px" font-family="TNYAdobeCaslonPro, 'Times New Roman', serif;" color="white">
          <h2 style="
          padding-top:14px;
          padding-bottom:8px; 
          color:#4D3060;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom:2px solid #4D3060; 
            
              font-size: 26px;
              line-height: 1.2; 
              font-weight: 400;
               
            ">Spotlight</h2>   
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="TNYAdobeCaslonPro, 'Times New Roman', serif;" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="
              font-size: 24px; 
              line-height: 1.2; 
              font-weight: 400;
              margin-top: 2px !important; 
            ">Record breaking speech</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/president-donald-trump-breaks-bill-clinton-record-joint-session-congress-speech.png" alt="President Donald Trump broke former President Bill Clinton's record for a Joint Session of Congress speech" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;">President Donald Trump broke former President Bill Clinton's record for a Joint Session of Congress speech. Credits: Jack Gruber/ USA Today</p>
        </mj-text>
        
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">President Trump gave his <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-05-03-2025-h1-1-first-address-to-congress?source=website" target="_blank">first address to Congress</a> since returning to office. It was the longest speech in congressional history. He praised his administration’s actions during the first six weeks and promised to reclaim the Panama Canal and acquire Greenland “one way or the other.” He also spoke about Europe and Ukraine, calling for an end to the war while questioning Europe’s financial contributions to the conflict. Additionally, he praised Elon Musk for his contributions.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">His speech highlighted key policies from his first month. These included tariffs, border security, gender issues, and federal government cutting. Trump announced new economic policies, including reciprocal tariffs, tax cuts, and a “Gold Card” program. He also signed two more executive orders. One bans gender-affirming care for minors, and the other mandates the death penalty for those convicted of killing police officers.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
  </mj-body>
